🧠 CORE GAME LOOP (What the player does)

1. Chest appears (from conveyor)

Has:
Tier (1–10)
Aura (or none)
Price

2. Player decision

Skip → new chest rolls
Buy → chest is taken

3. Chest is opened (via slot system)

Becomes a sword after a delay
Sword has:
Tier (based on chest RNG drift)
Aura (from chest)

4. Sword goes into a display slot

Generates passive income

5. Income accumulates

NOT instantly given
Stored as Pending Money

6. Player collects money

Walks over CashCollector
Receives all stored income

7. Repeat loop

Upgrade, replace swords, optimize slots
